{{version025}}

A few effects in the game call for the creation of a '''lesser demon''', most notably the monster spell [[Summon Minor Demon]] (but not [[Call Imp]], which has its own list).  This chooses a random [[Demon#Tier-5 Demons|tier-5 demon]] from the following list:

*{{monsterlink|Crimson imp}}
*{{monsterlink|Iron imp}}
*{{monsterlink|Quasit}}
*{{monsterlink|Shadow imp}}
*{{monsterlink|Ufetubus}}
*{{monsterlink|White imp}}

==History==
Prior to [[0.14]], the player could summon 7-11 lesser demons with the [[Demonic Horde]] spell.

